        "subject": "LU-8508 nodemap: release nodemap index obj if fail to register",
        "message": "LU-8508 nodemap: release nodemap index obj if fail to register\n\nIn nodemap_fs_init(), if nm_config_file_register() failed, we\nneed to release the object returned by nodemap_cache_find_create(),\nOtherwise, it will cause ASSERTION( atomic_read(&d->ld_ref) == 0 ).\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I04570244bacf820cfa375098431010145cde1df2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
